{
  "texts": [
    "During the splitting process, the images for the same patients were included in the same set to prevent the results from being biased.",
    "The same sets were used across both detection and classification tasks to guarantee fair evaluation for the whole model.",
    "INbreastThis dataset is composed of mammographic images that were produced using the FFDM technique.",
    "It includes 410 images in DICOM format for 115 cases with both views, Medio Lateral Oblique (MLO) and Carnio Caudal (CC).",
    "However, the dataset did not provide both views for each patient."
  ]
}